When NETZ Roadmap of 12 Power Plants has been built out and are operation, the real world Enterprises/Asset Value will be $6.5 Billion with annual dividends of $680M. The cashflows are then estimated to grow by 50% per year as the Roadmap grows and reinvestments are made.  •         For the total $374M scope of the NETZ Coin Roadmap, the initial asset value of NETZ Pre Developed Roadmap is $1.7 Billion ($374M in equity enables debt investments for the remaining amount up to $1.7 Billion).  •         NETZ will pay out strong dividends and cash flow to all token holders on a quarterly basis through blockchain technology enabling transparency of performance and financial metrics to NETZ Investors.  •         Buy Back Guarantee – NETZ offers it’s investors an escalating Buy Back Program over the first five years with a 100% return guarantee in Year 5 because of NETZ ability to create actual real world returns from the Renewable Energy Power Plants.  •         NETZ Soft Target is only $7,500,0000 USD in order to break ground on the first phase Power Plant in the Roadmap, which start generating cash flow in month 6. Investor returns will be identical, due to pro rata structure, whether $7.5M or the full $374M is raised.  •         Continuously and exponentially contribute to solving five of the major problems in the worlds, through utilization of disruptive and commercially proven technologies that generate employment opportunities, renewable and sustainable solutions, and highly dividend generating assets with high appreciation.
